re </em>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/opioid-dependence/references/\">Ford et al, 2011</a>], the Department of Health and the devolved administrations' guideline <em>Drug misuse and dependence: UK guidelines on clinical management </em>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/opioid-dependence/references/\">DH, 2017</a>], and the National Drug Strategy Australia (NDSA) <em>National guidelines for medication-assisted treatment of opioid dependence</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/opioid-dependence/references/\">NDSA, 2014</a>]. </p><!-- end field 9675a9ea-8367-4ca7-9c65-a74d00955f07 --><!-- end item ea4d5421-06c0-45b2-a6e0-a74d00955d7c -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}